    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been my trusty companion and is still running like a champ. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of love here and there, but overall it\u2019s in solid shape and super dependable. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to find a great new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
