    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S. This wide-body 996.2 is powered by the M96 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. The viscous-clutch AWD system provides exceptional mechanical grip and corner-exit stability. This example has undergone a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a recent bore scope inspection, confirming the integrity of the Nikasil-coated cylinders. The chassis remains taut with refreshed control arm bushings and factory-spec Bilstein dampers. Braking is handled by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, ensuring zero fade during spirited sessions. A communicative, driver-centric machine ready for its next apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Interior and exterior well-kept. Runs smooth. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
